scenes.description: Kureiji Ollie discusses her origins as a zombie and the meaning of her existence with Roberu Yukoku in a city setting.
Ollie walks alone, monologuing about her life. She encounters a wilted sunflower and unintentionally causes it to bloom through a mysterious power.
Performance of the song 'Juggernaut' by Kureiji Ollie on a stage set among ancient stone ruins.

subtitles.original: 話は長くなるけど...
subtitles.english: It's kind of a long story...

subtitles.original: 最近、自分の存在の理由が気になって...
subtitles.english: I've been thinking about my origins... You know, the reason why I became a zombie...

subtitles.original: あ、オリーの実家がラーメン屋に変わったから起きたんじゃないの？
subtitles.english: Isn't it because you sensed that your house turned into a ramen shop? Or so I heard.

subtitles.original: 違うよ！それはたまたま起きた時にラーメン屋だった！
subtitles.english: That was actually a coincidence! I happen to wake up and it already was a ramen shop...

subtitles.original: それでね...
subtitles.english: And you know?

subtitles.original: 自分の存在について考え始めて...
subtitles.english: The more I think about my existence...

subtitles.original: 自分の運命まで考えちゃって...
subtitles.english: The more I think about fate...

subtitles.original: なぜ運命がオリーを起こしたんだろう？
subtitles.english: Why did it make me live I wonder?

subtitles.original: 死んだ後に未練でもあるのかなあ？
subtitles.english: Why is my grave not the end of my chapter? Can't help it...

subtitles.original: そういうことがあったんだ。
subtitles.english: I see, so you've been having those thoughts...

subtitles.original: 大変だね。
subtitles.english: It must be hard for you to think about.

subtitles.original: でもたまに考えずにそのままにしておいたほうがいいこともあるのって知ってる？
subtitles.english: But you know, sometimes there are things that are best left as is...

subtitles.original: だから深く考えないで、そのうち答えが出てくるからさ。
subtitles.english: I don't think you need to ponder too much about it, surely the answer will come to you on it's own...

subtitles.original: そうだね。その通りだね！
subtitles.english: You know what... You're right senpai!

subtitles.original: 焦る必要がないし...
subtitles.english: I shouldn't rush too much...

subtitles.original: いつかきっと答えが出てくるはず！
subtitles.english: Surely I'll find out sooner or later!

subtitles.original: 役に立ってよかった。
subtitles.english: I'm glad I got to help you...

subtitles.original: じゃ、リハがあるから先に行ってくるね。
subtitles.english: Anyways, I have dance practice so I better take my leave now.

subtitles.original: うん！先輩本当にありがとう！
subtitles.english: I will! Thank you so much senpai!

subtitles.original: 元気でね、オリー！
subtitles.english: Take care, Ollie!

subtitles.original: 先輩の言った通りだ。
subtitles.english: He's right...

subtitles.original: 考えすぎなくていい。
subtitles.english: I shouldn't think about it too much...

subtitles.original: 必ず答えが出てくる。
subtitles.english: I should just take my time...

subtitles.original: Pada akhirnya, bukannya dapet jawaban, malah ngegabut ke mana-mana.
subtitles.english: In the end, I just wasted my day looking for an answer that I don't even know exists.

subtitles.original: Iofie-senpai sampai aku tinggalin lagi.
subtitles.english: I feel bad for bailing on dance practice with Iofie-senpai...

subtitles.original: Jadi gak enak aku.
subtitles.english: I gotta apologize later...

subtitles.original: Jawabannya bakal dateng sendiri... huh.
subtitles.english: The answer will come to me sooner or later, huh.

subtitles.original: Iya, moga-moga jawabannya gak ngaret datengnya, keburu meninggal lagi aku.
subtitles.english: I hope I won't have to wait too long that I get revived a second time.

subtitles.original: Andai ada petunjuk sedikit aja.

subtitles.original: Eh?

subtitles.original: Itu... bunga?

subtitles.original: Kok tumbuhnya di pinggir jalan sih? Aneh.
subtitles.english: What's it doing growing at a busy street like this? How weird.

subtitles.original: Ini tuh bukan tempat kamu bunga kecil.
subtitles.english: This isn't your place little daisy.

subtitles.original: Kamu seharusnya tumbuh di tempat lain.
subtitles.english: You belong somewhere else where...

subtitles.original: Kalo tumbuhnya di sini, yang ada kamu layu.
subtitles.english: If you were to stay, then you'll only wilt.

subtitles.original: Barusan... apa yang terjadi?
subtitles.english: W-What... Just... Happened...?

subtitles.original: Bunganya... mekar.
subtitles.english: It... Bloomed.

subtitles.original: Apa-apaan...
subtitles.english: What in the world...

subtitles.original: Yang barusan itu... aku?
subtitles.english: Did... I do that...?

subtitles.original: Jadi... inikah?
subtitles.english: ...Is this it...?
